                         RN: Ch. 9, Nilsson Ch. 16<p>

                  <li><b> Veteran day <p>

                </UL>
              </td>
              <td class="line">11-09</td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="line"><NOBR>Week 8</NOBR></td>

              <td class="outline">
                <UL>
                  <li><b>Planning:</b>
                         Logic-based planning, the situation calculus, the frame problem.<br>
                         RN: Ch. 11, Nilsson Ch. 21

                  <li>Planning: Planning systems, STRIP, regression planning,
                         search-based, and propositional-based.<br>
                         RN: Ch. 11, Nilsson Ch. 22 <p>.

                </UL>
              </td>
